      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is ideal for a dedicated restoration project or as a comprehensive parts donor. The engine is currently non-operational and does not turn over, and the body exhibits significant rust, particularly along the frame and lower panels. The interior shows heavy wear and will require a full overhaul. Please expect to tow this vehicle from its current location.",
