    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for anyone looking for honest transportation. The engine starts up consistently and handles city driving well, though potential buyers should note some minor fluid seepage and a suspension that feels a bit soft over bumps. The exterior has some visible clear coat fading and a few minor door dings, while the interior shows typical wear on the driver's seat and carpets. It is a solid, functional car that has been maintained for utility rather than show, making it a great value for someone who prioritizes mechanical function over cosmetic perfection.",
